# Pharmacy Management System — Comprehensive Testing Report

> **Date**: March 5, 2026  
> **Testing Method**: Static analysis (`dart analyze`) + deep manual code review  
> **Flutter SDK**: 3.27.3 (macOS permission issue prevented live runtime testing)  
> **Apps Tested**: Admin, User, Outlet, POS, Delivery Partner, Super Admin

---

## Static Analysis Summary

| App | Total Issues | Errors | Warnings | Info (Deprecations) |
|-----|-------------|--------|----------|-------------------|
| **Admin** | 2,756 | ~255 | ~0 | ~2,501 |
| **User** | 1,931 | ~190 | ~0 | ~1,741 |
| **Outlet** | 2,018 | ~221 | ~0 | ~1,797 |
| **POS** | 1,411 | ~272 | ~0 | ~1,139 |
| **Delivery Partner** | 1,038 | ~81 | ~0 | ~957 |
| **Super Admin** | 2,755 | ~261 | ~0 | ~2,494 |

> [!NOTE]
> Error counts are inflated due to `dart analyze` (not `flutter analyze`) being unable to resolve Flutter framework imports. True compile errors are a subset. Deprecation warnings (~info) are real and actionable.

---

## 🔴 Application 1: Admin App

### Modules Reviewed
`auth` · `dashboard` · `inventory` · `orders` · `outlets` · `vendors` · `financial` · `banners` · `refunds` · `subscription` · `settings` · `terminals` · `promo_codes` · `offers` · `users` · `permissions` · `activity_log` · `drivers` · `product_analytics` · `customer_analytics` · `kyc_documents`

### Bugs & Errors

| # | Severity | File | Issue |
|---|----------|------|-------|
| 1 | 🔴 Critical | [main.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/main.dart#L11-L13) | **Hardcoded Supabase credentials** — URL and anon key are embedded in source code as fallback constants. If committed to a public repo, this exposes the backend. |
| 2 | 🟡 Medium | [login_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/features/auth/view/login_view.dart#L126-L128) | **Weak email validation** — Only checks `contains('@')`. Accepts invalid emails like `@`, `a@`, `@b`. Should use regex pattern. |
| 3 | 🟡 Medium | [login_viewmodel.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/login_viewmodel.dart#L104) | **Uses `print()` for error logging** — Should use `debugPrint()` for production safety. `print()` statements leak info in release builds. |
| 4 | 🟡 Medium | [login_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/features/auth/view/login_view.dart) | **Login view doesn't use LoginViewModel** — The view directly calls `Supabase.instance.client.auth.signInWithPassword()` instead of going through the ViewModel. The ViewModel with session logging/activity tracking is bypassed. |
| 5 | 🟡 Medium | [orders_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/features/orders/view/orders_view.dart#L186-L188) | **Debug print statements left in production code** — Lines 187, 195, 241 use `print()` for debugging. |
| 6 | 🟢 Low | [orders_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/features/orders/view/orders_view.dart#L653) | **Hardcoded text color** — Pagination "Showing X to Y" text uses `Colors.black` instead of theme-aware colors. Broken in dark mode. |

### UI/UX Issues

| # | Issue |
|---|-------|
| 1 | Login page references `assets/logo.png` — if missing, shows broken image |
| 2 | Admin Shell/Sidebar navigation has 21+ routes — may feel overwhelming; consider grouping with sub-menus |
| 3 | Orders table uses fixed `flex` column widths — may cause truncation on smaller screens |
| 4 | Error page (`errorBuilder` in router) shows plain text "Page not found" — no styling or navigation back |

### Missing Validations

| # | Issue |
|---|-------|
| 1 | Password field has no minimum length validation |
| 2 | No rate limiting on login attempts (client-side) |
| 3 | [add_product_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/features/inventory/view/add_product_view.dart) accepts negative numbers for price and stock quantity (no min value validation) |
| 4 | Order status update has no confirmation dialog — accidental clicks can change order state |

### Suggested Enhancements

- Move Supabase credentials to `.env` file (already partially done, but fallback exposes secrets)
- Add [copyWith()](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/outlet/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#29-46) method to [OrderItem](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/features/orders/view/orders_view.dart#10-112) model to avoid manual field-by-field copying (line 215-232)
- Separate model/state/notifier from [orders_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/features/orders/view/orders_view.dart) (1032 lines in one file with MVC mixed)
- Add loading indicators per-row when updating order status
- Add offline error handling / retry with exponential backoff

