## 🟢 Application 2: User App

### Modules Reviewed
`auth` · `cart` · `home` · `address` · `map` · `notifications` · `offers` · `splash` · `subscription`

### Bugs & Errors

| # | Severity | File | Issue |
|---|----------|------|-------|
| 1 | 🔴 Critical | [auth_viewmodel.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#L115-L123) | **Hardcoded Supabase URL + anon key inline** — Embedded directly in [sendPhoneOtp()](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#111-144) and [verifyOtp()](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#145-213) methods using `String.fromEnvironment` with hardcoded defaults. |
| 2 | 🔴 Critical | [auth_viewmodel.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#L261-L262) | **Sets `phone_verified: true` during Google Sign-In** — Phone is never verified during Google login, but profile is created with `phone_verified: true`. This is a data integrity bug. |
| 3 | 🟡 Medium | [login_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/view/login_view.dart#L433) | **Placeholder text "Name of the portal"** — Line 433 displays `"New to Name of the portal? "` instead of the actual app name. Should say "New to A+ Med App?". |
| 4 | 🟡 Medium | [login_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/view/login_view.dart#L437-L439) | **Uses `Navigator.push` instead of GoRouter** — The "Sign Up" link navigates using `Navigator.push(MaterialPageRoute(...))` while the rest of the app uses [GoRouter](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/core/router/app_router.dart#186-199). This bypasses route guards and creates inconsistent navigation behavior. |
| 5 | 🟡 Medium | [auth_viewmodel.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#L233) | **Force-unwrap on `auth.currentUser!`** — After Google sign-in, `currentUser` is force-unwrapped without null check. If auth state isn't propagated immediately, this could crash. |
| 6 | 🟡 Medium | [auth_viewmodel.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#L272-L273) | **Hardcoded address comparison** — `'Gandhi Nagar, CBE'` is hardcoded in source code to decide whether to update a user's address. |
| 7 | 🟢 Low | [auth_viewmodel.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#L219-L220) | **Hardcoded Google OAuth Client ID** — The Google `serverClientId` is hardcoded. Should be in environment config. |

### UI/UX Issues

| # | Issue |
|---|-------|
| 1 | Login page has a hardcoded green `Color(0xFF00A86B)` that doesn't respect theme/admin settings |
| 2 | Google Sign-In button uses a generic `Icons.g_mobiledata` icon instead of the official Google logo |
| 3 | Mobile login layout has no scroll indicator — users may not realize form extends below the fold |
| 4 | "Forgot Password" action doesn't validate email format before sending — only checks if empty |

### Missing Validations

| # | Issue |
|---|-------|
| 1 | Phone number validation only checks length (10 digits) — doesn't validate numeric-only input |
| 2 | Password minimum is 6 characters — no uppercase/special character requirements (may be intentional for pharmacy customers) |
| 3 | Signup doesn't validate that email isn't already registered before attempting signup |
| 4 | No OTP resend cooldown timer visible to user |

### Suggested Enhancements

- Replace placeholder text "Name of the portal" with dynamic app name from settings
- Use [GoRouter](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/core/router/app_router.dart#186-199) consistently for all navigation
- Add proper Google logo asset for the sign-in button
- Add biometric / fingerprint login option for returning users
- Add profile completeness indicator post-signup

