## 🔵 Application 3: Outlet App

### Modules Reviewed
`auth` · `customers` · `dashboard` · `devices` · `drivers` · `employees` · `expenses` · `grn` · `inventory` · `leaves` · `navigationbars` · `notifications` · `orders` · `profile` · `purchase_orders` · `vendors`

### Bugs & Errors

| # | Severity | File | Issue |
|---|----------|------|-------|
| 1 | 🟡 Medium | [login_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/outlet/lib/features/auth/view/login_view.dart#L177) | **Forgot Password is a TODO** — The "Forgot Password?" button has `// TODO: Implement forgot password` with no implementation. Users cannot recover their password. |
| 2 | 🟡 Medium | [login_view.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/outlet/lib/features/auth/view/login_view.dart#L118-L126) | **Weak email validation** — Only checks `contains('@')`. Same issue as Admin app. |
| 3 | 🟢 Low | [auth_viewmodel.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/outlet/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#L88-L94) | **Initialization timeout uses magic delay** — 1500ms `Future.delayed` to determine if no session exists. On slow connections, this may show login prematurely while a session is still being restored. |
| 4 | 🟢 Low | [auth_viewmodel.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/outlet/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#L50-L55) | **Auth subscription never disposed** — `_authSubscription` is created in [build()](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/admin/lib/main.dart#46-103) but the [Notifier](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/user/lib/features/auth/viewmodel/auth_viewmodel.dart#24-598) class has no dispose mechanism. Could cause memory leaks. |

### UI/UX Issues

| # | Issue |
|---|-------|
| 1 | Uses generic pharmacy icon instead of a branded logo |
| 2 | Multi-step registration (documents, images, outlet info, staff) — no step progress indicator visible |
| 3 | Signup flow goes to `/register` route if outlet not registered — no clear indication of what registration entails |

### Missing Validations

| # | Issue |
|---|-------|
| 1 | Forgot password is completely unimplemented |
| 2 | No re-authentication required for sensitive operations (e.g., employee management) |
| 3 | Registration model validation may not check all required document formats |

### Suggested Enhancements

- Implement forgot password functionality
- Add registration progress stepper with clear visual indicators
- Add outlet onboarding walkthrough for first-time users
- Add document upload validation (file type, size limits)

