## 🟣 Application 5: Delivery Partner App

### Modules Reviewed
`auth` · `home` · `navigation` · `order_request` · `orders` · `profile` · `tracking`

### Bugs & Errors

| # | Severity | File | Issue |
|---|----------|------|-------|
| 1 | 🟡 Medium | [login_screen.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/deliver_partner/lib/features/auth/presentation/screens/login_screen.dart#L379-L381) | **"Apply to be a Partner" button is a placeholder** — `onPressed` has empty body `{ // Placeholder — partner signup }`. Button is visible but does nothing. |
| 2 | 🟡 Medium | [login_screen.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/deliver_partner/lib/features/auth/presentation/screens/login_screen.dart#L406-L408) | **"Need help logging in?" is a placeholder** — Same issue, empty `onPressed`. |
| 3 | 🟡 Medium | [login_screen.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/deliver_partner/lib/features/auth/presentation/screens/login_screen.dart#L296-L312) | **Terms of Service and Privacy Policy links are non-clickable** — Displayed as styled `TextSpan` but have no `TapGestureRecognizer`. Users see colored text that looks clickable but isn't. |
| 4 | 🟡 Medium | [login_screen.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/deliver_partner/lib/features/auth/presentation/screens/login_screen.dart#L75-L86) | **No phone number validation** — Only checks `phone.isNotEmpty`. Accepts letters, special characters, or single digits. No 10-digit validation. |
| 5 | 🟢 Low | [auth_repository.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/deliver_partner/lib/features/auth/data/auth_repository.dart#L32-L33) | **Throws raw string instead of Exception** — `throw e.message` throws a String, not an Exception. Inconsistent error handling pattern. |
| 6 | 🟢 Low | [login_screen.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/deliver_partner/lib/features/auth/presentation/screens/login_screen.dart#L218) | **Empty hint text** — Phone field has `hintText: ''`. Should show placeholder like "Enter your mobile number". |

### UI/UX Issues

| # | Issue |
|---|-------|
| 1 | Login screen is hardcoded to white background — doesn't support dark mode |
| 2 | Non-functional buttons ("Apply to be a Partner", "Need help") create poor user experience |
| 3 | Decorative circle rings painter ([_CircleRingsPainter](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/deliver_partner/lib/features/auth/presentation/screens/login_screen.dart#12-56)) draws circles partially outside the viewport |
| 4 | Uses `Navigator.push` for OTP screen — inconsistent with any potential router setup |
| 5 | Country code `+91` is hardcoded — no international support |

### Missing Validations

| # | Issue |
|---|-------|
| 1 | Phone number has no format/length validation |
| 2 | OTP field may not validate 6-digit format |
| 3 | Document upload ([uploadPartnerDocument](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/deliver_partner/lib/features/auth/data/auth_repository.dart#178-205)) has no file size or file type validation |
| 4 | Vehicle number format not validated |

### Suggested Enhancements

- Implement partner signup flow or remove the button
- Add actual Terms of Service and Privacy Policy screens with `TapGestureRecognizer`
- Add phone number mask/formatting (10 digits, numeric only)
- Add dark mode support
- Implement "Need help" — link to support chat or FAQ

