## ⚫ Application 6: Super Admin App

### Modules Reviewed
`activity_log` · `auth` · `banners` · `customer_analytics` · `dashboard` · `drivers` · `financial` · `inventory` · `kyc_documents` · `offers` · `orders` · `outlets` · `permissions` · `product_analytics` · `promo_codes` · `refunds` · `settings` · `subscription` · `terminals` · `users` · `vendors`

### Bugs & Errors

| # | Severity | File | Issue |
|---|----------|------|-------|
| 1 | 🔴 Critical | All files | **Near-identical codebase to Admin app** — The `super_admin` app is an almost exact copy of `admin` with 2,755 issues (vs Admin's 2,756). Both `super_admin/` and `super-admin/` directories exist, suggesting a duplication/migration issue. The `super-admin/` directory lacks a [pubspec.yaml](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/pubspec.yaml) and appears incomplete. |
| 2 | 🔴 Critical | [main.dart](file:///Users/srinivasanp/Zenthink/Projects/pharmacy_management/apps/super_admin/lib/main.dart) | Same hardcoded Supabase credentials as Admin app |
| 3 | 🟡 Medium | Entire codebase | All bugs identified in the Admin app apply identically to Super Admin |

### UI/UX Issues

Same as Admin app — see Application 1.

### Suggested Enhancements

- **Merge admin and super_admin into a single codebase** with role-based feature toggling
- Remove the duplicate `super-admin/` directory
- If separate access levels are required, use a shared package with role-based UI rendering

---

## Cross-Cutting Issues (All Apps)

### 🔒 Security

| # | Severity | Issue | Apps Affected |
|---|----------|-------|---------------|
| 1 | 🔴🔴 | **Plaintext passwords** in employees table | POS |
| 2 | 🔴 | **Hardcoded Supabase credentials** in source code | All 6 apps |
| 3 | 🔴 | **Hardcoded Google OAuth Client ID** | User |
| 4 | 🟡 | **No client-side rate limiting** on auth attempts | All apps |
| 5 | 🟡 | **`print()` statements** leak info in release builds | Admin, POS |

### 📐 Architecture

| # | Issue | Apps Affected |
|---|-------|---------------|
| 1 | Model + State + Notifier + View in single 1000+ line files | Admin, POS |
| 2 | Mixed navigation (GoRouter + Navigator.push) | User, POS, Delivery |
| 3 | Inconsistent auth patterns (Supabase Auth vs custom table) | POS uses employees table instead of Supabase Auth |
| 4 | Super Admin is a fork of Admin instead of shared code | Admin, Super Admin |
| 5 | No shared core package for common models/utilities | All apps |

### 🎨 Deprecation Warnings (All Apps)

| API | Replacement | Occurrences |
|-----|------------|-------------|
| `Color.withOpacity(x)` | `Color.withValues(alpha: x)` | ~500+ across all apps |
| `DropdownButtonFormField(value: x)` | `DropdownButtonFormField(initialValue: x)` | ~50+ |
| `Radio(groupValue: x, onChanged: y)` | `RadioGroup` widget | ~10+ in Admin/Super Admin |

