## Priority Action Items

```diff
+ [P0 - CRITICAL] Fix POS plaintext password storage — implement bcrypt hashing
+ [P0 - CRITICAL] Move ALL Supabase credentials to .env files
+ [P1 - HIGH] Implement Forgot Password in Outlet app
+ [P1 - HIGH] Fix "Name of the portal" placeholder in User app
+ [P1 - HIGH] Fix phone_verified=true bug in User Google Sign-In
+ [P1 - HIGH] Fix duplicate property assignments in POS login_view.dart
+ [P2 - MEDIUM] Implement placeholder buttons in Delivery Partner app
+ [P2 - MEDIUM] Add proper phone/email validation across all apps
+ [P2 - MEDIUM] Make Terms of Service links clickable in Delivery Partner
+ [P2 - MEDIUM] Merge Admin and Super Admin into shared codebase
+ [P3 - LOW] Replace all withOpacity() calls with withValues()
+ [P3 - LOW] Replace print() with debugPrint() across all apps
+ [P3 - LOW] Refactor large single-file modules into proper MVC structure
```
